Overall: The game features a lot of stuff. Little repetitive but enjoyable. Love how the online community keeps signs and other stuff to help you out around the world...for sure its not for anyone but i really recommend it, if you want a weird ass story to mind fuck you a little, go for it. Thanks Kojima and 505 to push for a port to pc, and not keeping it exclusive to the ps4 <3
